{"tid":2043031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"急撤留學生？ 中國官方突通知留美學生搭臨時航班回國","createTime":"2020-05-30T06:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T07:19:05.000Z","uid":339805,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d69f252d5250879a1ef81b8404b8a16c6071f0","tid":2043031,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/30/phpaP0Ibh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F30%2FphpaP0Ibh.jpg&h=7941410d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普29日在白宮記者會上宣布，禁止與解放軍有關的中國留學生和研究人員入境美國。中國駐美大使館今（30）日發布通知，將安排留學生搭乘臨時航班自美國華盛頓返回中國深圳。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國駐美大使館根據中國外交部部署，安排中國國航臨時包機。中國國航將透過中國駐美使館所提供的名單，通知符合資格的留學生購買機票。中國留學生包機預計將在美東時間6月4日下午，從華盛頓杜勒斯國際機場（Dulles International Airport）起飛。乘客除須符合條件外，也需要根據中國駐美使館規定，做好健康碼的填寫，健康碼異常者將無法登機，虛報填寫恐面臨相關法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐美大使館通知也提到，近日多名中國公民反映，在出境時被美邊境海關長時間盤問，並檢查隨身攜帶的手機、電腦等電子設備，部分人員的電子設備被執法人員暫扣。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮29日宣布，為防止美國經濟、智慧財產遭中國竊取，危害國家安全，6月1日起將限制中國公民簽證，禁止與中國解放軍有關係的留學生和研究人員入境。"},{"pid":"6585f6461307c007f4fa517493e0844e8647e8f9","tid":2043031,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"6月4日<br />\n乜支那出得呢個數字既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076e9677dc10dc0a20bc0b70b683167a72dbb30c","tid":2043031,"uid":111375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:04:24.000Z","msg":"返去祖國懷抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55cd93a35bcc9438fa6405f8812802c561c873e","tid":2043031,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"被回國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad2b82b203189d9fe3b5cab29e90c7ae6806c12","tid":2043031,"uid":272271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"俾左咁多錢學費換唔到畢業證書添"},{"pid":"0df6c16312afbf21234ecb7a420c6fd5b5965167","tid":2043031,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6585f6461307c007f4fa517493e0844e8647e8f9","tid":2043031,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"6月4日<br />\n乜支那出得呢個數字既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4065d164e9f3084ecd97cc90bfa090f900027ccb","tid":2043031,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:17:52.000Z","msg":"應該係諗住以大批人數幫班臥底走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係老美遂個查起上黎實仆街"},{"pid":"2e8f01b2f8a3e2aff2dfbdc2e65b99c08ac60d18","tid":2043031,"uid":301100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"又話十萬一張飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}